<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>0</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>4790</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>[g@Five hundred years passed.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>4791</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>8454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>Wukong stayed trapped under the mountain.@g]</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>8455</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14086</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>A thick layer of moss covered the monkey.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14087</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20048</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>One day Buddha sat in the Thunderclap Monastery in the Western Paradise.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20049</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>He was talking to his students.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29322</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"The people in the East, in the Tang Empire, need our help," said Buddha.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>[g@"They lie, cheat, and steal.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37244</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>They are greedy and constantly fighting."@g]</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37245</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40663</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>[g@He held up a bundle of scrolls.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40664</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43544</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"These are the True Scriptures.@g]</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43545</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47875</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>They will teach the people in the East to act better."</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47876</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50529</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"Wonderful," said one student.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50530</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53844</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"Let's bring the scriptures to the Tang Empire."</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53845</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55898</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>[g@Buddha shook his head.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55899</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58625</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"No," he said.@g]</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58626</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64424</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"A true believer—a monk—needs to come here to get them.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64425</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>Will anyone go to the East to find a worthy monk?"</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69170</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72565</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>[g@Guanyin stepped forward.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72566</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77399</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"I will go."@g]</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77400</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>The Tang Emperor smiled as his head monk read to a small group of people.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87341</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>The monk was reading old religious texts.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87342</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89957</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>A woman interrupted the monk.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89958</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94345</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"Why are you reading those old texts?" she asked.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94346</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"Don't you know about the True Scriptures?"</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101122</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>[g@The emperor stood up.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101123</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104983</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"How dare you interrupt my—"@g]</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108439</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>[g@"It's okay," said the monk.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108440</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117639</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>He walked over to the woman.@g]</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117640</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119674</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"What are the True Scriptures?"</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119675</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123640</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>[g@The woman looked at the monk carefully.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123641</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126739</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"They contain many lessons.@g]</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126740</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131738</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>People who learn the lessons never have to suffer again."</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131739</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"Do you have them here?" asked the monk.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137225</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>[g@"No," said the woman.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137226</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141244</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"They are with Buddha in the Western Paradise.@g]</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141245</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145859</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>Someone must travel to the Thunderclap Monastery to get them.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145860</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150750</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>But only a true believer may make the journey."</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150751</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154544</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>[g@She took a robe out of her bag.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154545</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158823</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"Put this on."@g]</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158824</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161423</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>The monk put on the robe.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161424</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164472</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>[g@Beams of light shone from it.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164473</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166698</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>The emperor gasped.@g]</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166699</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171066</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>[g@"You are a true believer," said the woman.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171067</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174748</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"Will you make the journey?"@g]</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174749</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179505</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"Yes," said the monk, looking down at the glowing robe.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179506</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"It will be an honor."</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186008</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"The journey will be very difficult," said the woman.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186009</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190929</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"Wide rivers and steep mountains will block your path.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190930</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197980</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>Fierce creatures and evil demons will try to attack you.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197981</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>But don't fear—you will have help from me."</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207458</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>Suddenly the room filled with blinding light.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207459</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211928</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>The woman rose into the air and changed form.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211929</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"It's the bodhisattva Guanyin!" someone cried.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215754</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219296</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>The emperor and everyone else in the room bowed.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219297</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226416</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>Guanyin rose higher and then disappeared.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226417</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229924</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>The next morning there was a huge feast.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>The Tang Emperor sat next to the monk.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238725</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"Your journey will help our empire greatly," said the emperor.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238726</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243328</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"No longer will our people suffer or treat each other badly.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243329</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247509</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>From now on, I will think of you as my brother.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247510</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250781</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>You will be called the Tang Monk."</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250782</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254394</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"Thank you, Your Majesty," said the Tang Monk.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254395</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258394</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"How long will the journey take?" asked the emperor.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258395</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266476</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"I will return in a few years," said the monk.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266477</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>Later that day the Tang Monk got ready for his journey.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277760</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>[g@He put the special robe into a bag.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277761</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282340</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>He put dried foods into another bag.@g]</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282341</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286328</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>A big crowd gathered to say good-bye.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286329</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"Good luck, my brother," said the Tang Emperor.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291116</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300592</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>The Tang Monk climbed onto a horse and rode toward the West.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300593</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>He had traveled for over a month when he came to a big mountain.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310480</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>Slowly his horse walked up a steep trail.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310481</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314193</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>[g@"I have a bad feeling," said the Tang Monk.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314194</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316412</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>He looked around uneasily.@g]</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>316413</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319689</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"I hope there aren't any demons here."</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319690</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>329512</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>Suddenly a voice boomed, "Who is walking on my mountain?"</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>